item.title: About
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Typical Mediterranean gourmet food in a charming ambience

 

Experience the historic and elegant architecture of this palace. High arched ceilings, wooden décor and old memorabilia adorn Castelletti Salumeria & Patisserie, giving it a quaint and homely feeling. Otherwise, the courtyard which provides an equally charming and tranquil ambience for al fresco dining.

 

Every single dish served at the Salumeria is prepared fresh on the day. The Salumeria outlet caters for quick, healthy lunches and snacks at very low prices. All the products on display within the Salumeria can be consumed within the Salumeria or in the palazzo’s courtyard or even purchased for home use.

The menu allows patrons to select from a wide choice of salads and antipasti made with the gourmet products on display, or even design their own antipasto by choosing their preferred ingredients and have our Italian salumeria chef prepare the dish to order.

Our friendly staff will be able to assist you in all your enquiries about the Salumeria’s wine and food specialties of the day.
